-- CORRECTION: B&L approves Warburg Pincus buyout
-- 
-- Fri Sep 21, 2007 12:26pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/09/21/us-bauschlomb-buyout-corrected-idUSKRA15876620070921

 

 (Company corrected closing date from third quarter to fourth) 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shareholders of Bausch & Lomb Inc BOL.N approved a proposed $3.67 billion takeover by private equity firm Warburg Pincus on Friday, the eye care company said. Over two thirds of the total shares outstanding voted in favor of the deal, the company said, which is expected to close early in the fourth quarter.